<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:11:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际货币基金组织表示，二十国集团新兴经济体的冲击打击了富裕国家的增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/shocks-g20-emerging-economies-hit-rich-world-growth-imf-says-2024-04-09/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周二发布的一份报告称，二十国集团新兴经济体的国内冲击日益影响富裕国家的增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/shocks-g20-emerging-economies-hit-rich-world-growth-imf-says-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>美特使：美国将改变日本指挥姿态以增强威慑力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-change-japan-command-posture-boost-deterrence-face-china-us-envoy-2024-04-09/</link><description>美国驻日本大使周二表示，美国将从根本上改变日本计划中的新军事指挥中心的军事指挥姿态，以便在面对中国压力时能够更好地协调并增强威慑力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 13:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-change-japan-command-posture-boost-deterrence-face-china-us-envoy-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将对中国风电场涡轮机供应商展开调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-investigate-chinese-turbine-suppliers-wind-parks-2024-04-09/</link><description>欧盟委员会对中国供应商向欧洲风电场提供涡轮机的补贴展开新调查，这是其针对中国清洁技术产品制造商采取的最新行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 12:46:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-investigate-chinese-turbine-suppliers-wind-parks-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟领导人在峰会上要求全面推动竞争力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-leaders-demand-sweeping-competitiveness-drive-summit-2024-04-09/</link><description>根据路透社看到的结论草案，欧盟领导人将利用下周的峰会呼吁采取果断行动，以确保欧盟在全球舞台上的长期竞争力和领导地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-leaders-demand-sweeping-competitiveness-drive-summit-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军上将称中国试图通过武力获得空间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-gain-space-through-force-us-admiral-says-2024-04-09/</link><description>美国一位高级海军上将周二表示，中国在南海的行动是其试图通过武力获取领土空间的一个例子，并且正在破坏该地区的稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:47:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-trying-gain-space-through-force-us-admiral-says-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>在中国设有子公司的跨国公司受到更便宜的人民币融资的诱惑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-firms-with-china-units-tempted-by-cheaper-renminbi-funding-2024-04-09/</link><description>拥有中国业务的跨国公司越来越多地发行人民币债券来为在华业务融资，这是六年来首次比以美元融资更便宜。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:17:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-firms-with-china-units-tempted-by-cheaper-renminbi-funding-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：大宗商品价格扰乱通胀观点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行加速中国财富扩张，有望实现招聘目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-accelerate-china-wealth-expansion-track-meet-hiring-target-2024-04-09/</link><description>汇丰银行全球财富主管表示，尽管面临经济逆风，汇丰银行仍计划加速在中国扩张财富业务，并有望在明年将其员工人数增加近一倍，同时推进其亚洲支点战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:14:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-accelerate-china-wealth-expansion-track-meet-hiring-target-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>克里姆林宫表示普京和习近平计划会面，但没有给出时间表</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-putin-xi-plan-meet-gives-no-time-frame-2024-04-09/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯总统普京和中国国家主席习近平计划进行接触，但没有给出普京可能访问北京的时间表。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:55:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-putin-xi-plan-meet-gives-no-time-frame-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>舒尔茨出访前研究显示德国经济仍依赖中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ahead-scholz-trip-study-shows-german-economy-still-dependent-china-2024-04-09/</link><description>德国经济研究所周二的一项研究显示，尽管德国经济努力向其他市场多元化，但其许多产品和原材料仍然高度依赖中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:44:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ahead-scholz-trip-study-shows-german-economy-still-dependent-china-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月份新增人民币贷款反弹，预计将出台更多刺激措施 - 路透调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinas-march-new-yuan-loans-seen-rebounding-more-stimulus-expected-2024-04-09/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国新增人民币贷款预计将在 3 月份从 2 月份的大幅下降中反弹，因为央行在未来几个月将推出更多刺激措施的预期下寻求提振经济增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/chinas-march-new-yuan-loans-seen-rebounding-more-stimulus-expected-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯中止从东方航天发射场发射安加拉-A5太空火箭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-aborts-launch-angara-a5-space-rocket-vostochny-cosmodrome-2024-04-09/</link><description>周二，由于技术故障，俄罗斯被迫中止了安加拉-A5火箭在东方航天发射场的试射，距离原定发射时间只有几分钟。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-aborts-launch-angara-a5-space-rocket-vostochny-cosmodrome-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷与 ClearMotion 合作提供平稳的悬架技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-partners-with-clearmotion-its-smooth-suspension-tech-2024-04-09/</link><description>两家公司周二表示，德国豪华汽车制造商保时捷已与 ClearMotion 合作，验证这家美国初创公司的主动悬架技术和路读软件，并签署了技术许可协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-partners-with-clearmotion-its-smooth-suspension-tech-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>金管局首席执行官表示，香港正在考虑“深化”与中国的一些联系计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hkma-ceo-says-hong-kong-considering-deepening-some-connect-schemes-with-china-2024-04-09/</link><description>香港金融管理局（金管局）首席执行官余伟文周二表示，正在考虑深化香港与中国大陆之间的一些投资联系计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:58:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hkma-ceo-says-hong-kong-considering-deepening-some-connect-schemes-with-china-2024-04-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国第一季度电动汽车销量增速创一年新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-rise-57-yy-march-2024-04-09/</link><description>周二的行业数据显示，随着以比亚迪为首的汽车制造商加大折扣力度并提供融资工具以促进销量，中国 3 月份电动乘用车销量同比增长 10.5%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-rise-57-yy-march-2024-04-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>